1. *Zeleno* lišće pokriva travnjak. (Green leaves cover the lawn.)
2. Volim *zeleni* čaj. (I love green tea.)
3. Prošle godine sam kupio *zelenog* psa. (Last year I bought a green dog.)
4. *Zelenom* bojom sam obojio zidove u dnevnoj sobi. (I painted the walls in the living room with green color.)
5. Kada sam se vozio kroz šumu, vidio sam *zeleni* kombi parkiran pored puta. (When I was driving through the forest, I saw a green van parked beside the road.)
6. *Zeleniš* u mom dvorištu je prekrasan. (The greenery in my yard is beautiful.)
7. Jutros sam uživao u *zelenom* smoothieju. (This morning I enjoyed a green smoothie.)
8. *Zeleni* luk je ukusan u salati. (Green onion is tasty in a salad.)
9. Nisam siguran koje su mi omiljene *zelene* boje. (I'm not sure what my favorite shades of green are.)
10. Stavio sam *zeleni* kaput jer je vani hladno. (I put on my green coat because it's cold outside.)

Note: In Serbian language, the adjective "zeleno" (green) can also be used as a noun to refer to the color green in general. Additionally, the word "zeleniš" refers to a place where there is a lot of vegetation or greenery.